    "Basic of web development\n",
    "\n",
    "Telephonic network to Arpanet : -> The evolution form telephonic network ,which enabled voice communication to arpanet in the 1960s introduced packets-switching techonology for data sharing between computers\n",
    "\n",
    "Arpanet To Internet And WWW -> Arpanet expanded into the internet,connecting global network,while the world wide web(WWW) in 1989 provided a hyperlinked platform for accessing information online\n",
    "\n",
    "CLient Server Architechture  :  The WWW operates on a client server model .where client(browsers) send request to server hosting website,enabling dynamuc interaction and data exchange"
