    "HTTP REQUEST\n",
    "--> An HTTP request is a message sent by client (such as web browser) to a server,asking for a specifuc resource or action .IT consist od a request line (HTTP method.URL,and version) ,Headers(metadata about the request) and an optional body(data sent with methods like POST or PUT).This Structure allows the server to process and respond with the requested content(Look for FLow digram)"
   ]
  },
