   "source": [
    "HTTP Response\n",
    "--> An HTTP response is sent the server to the client in reply to an HTTP request.It consists of status line(HTTP Version,status code,and message), header(Providing metadata like content type and lenght),and an optional body(Contaning the requested data or content),This structure enables the client to interpret the servers response and display the appropriate content(Look for flow digram)"
   ]
  },
  {
