    "HTTP and HTTPS structure\n",
    "HTTP:\n",
    "\n",
    "Client–Server, request–response protocol\n",
    "\n",
    "Structure:\n",
    "\n",
    "Request/Response Line\n",
    "Headers\n",
    "Blank line\n",
    "Body (optional)\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "Data sent in plain text\n",
    "Uses port 80\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "HTTPS:\n",
    "\n",
    "HTTP over TLS/SSL\n",
    "\n",
    "Same request–response structure as HTTP\n",
    "\n",
    "Data is encrypted\n",
    "\n",
    "Uses port 443"
