    "Building up flask app\n",
    "1]App.py=> Main flask application\n",
    "2]templates/=> directory for html templates (in this case,index.html)\n",
    "3]static/=>Directory for static files(css,js,images) for this basic example,you dont need to add anything\n",
    "4]requirenment.txt=> List of python dependencies(eg.flask)\n",
    "config.py=>Configuration settings for your app(optional for simple projects)"
   ]
  },
  {
