   "id": "59937a64-dd38-4b02-9b33-4718567b601c",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Routing and URL Mapping\n",
    "    1]Static Routing->Static routing maps fixed URLs to specific view function.These routes do not change and are commonly used for static pages like the home page or about page\n",
    "\n",
    "    2]Dynamic Routing->Dynamiic routing enables URLs to accpet variable parts (parameters) that are passed to the view function.These are useful for user-specific content or data-driven pages\n",
    "\n",
    "    3]Adding Routes using add_url_rule-> Flask's add_url_rule method allows you to define routes programmatically.This is useful when you want more control or reuse functions ashandlers for multiple routes\n",
    "\n",
    "    4]Redirecting URL-> Flask provides the redirect() function to send users from one URL to another.This is useful for legacy URLs or when pages are moved.\n",
    "\n",
    "    5]Error Handling->Error handling ensures the application gracefully responds to invaild request or internal errors.Flask allows defining custom error pages using @app.errorhandler"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "raw",
   "id": "b7c870e5-12e8-4a53-945d-e132955941ab",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "from flask import Flask,render_template,redirect,url_for,jsonify\n",
    "\n",
    "app=Flask(__name__)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Static routing\n",
    "@app.route(\"/hello\")\n",
    "def hello_world():\n",
    "    return \"Hello world\"\n",
    "\n",
    "@app.route(\"/\")\n",
    "def home():\n",
    "    return \"Welcome to the home page!!\"\n",
    "\n",
    "@app.route(\"/about\")\n",
    "def about():\n",
    "    return \"This is about page\"\n",
    "\n",
    "#dynamic routing\n",
    "@app.route(\"/user/<username>\")\n",
    "def user(username):\n",
    "    return f\"Welcome user {username}!!\"\n",
    "\n",
    "@app.route(\"/post/<int:post_id>\")\n",
    "def post_number(post_id):\n",
    "    return f\"Your id is {post_id}\"\n",
    "\n",
    "#url rule handler\n",
    "def contact():\n",
    "    return f\"This is contact page\"\n",
    "app.add_url_rule(\"/contact\",view_func=contact)\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "# Redirecting url\n",
    "@app.route(\"/new-home\")\n",
    "def new_home():\n",
    "    return redirect(url_for('home'))\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "#Error handling\n",
    "@app.errorhandler(404)\n",
    "def not_found(e):\n",
    "    return jsonify({\n",
    "        \"error\":\"404 not found\",\n",
    "        \"message\":\"The requested URL was not found on th server.\"\n",
    "                }),404\n",
    "\n",
    "@app.errorhandler(500)\n",
    "def notfound(e):\n",
    "    return f\"An internal server error occurred .plese try agian later\",500\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "if __name__==\"__main__\":\n",
    "    app.run(debug=True)"
   ]
  },
